Package fi.abo.kogni.soile2.projecthandling.projectElements

Interface Element

All Superinterfaces:
AccessElement
All Known Implementing Classes:
ElementBase, Experiment, Project, Task
public interface Element extends AccessElement
Objects that implement this class reflect elements in a database that allow linking to a gitRepository. They also store all Versions
Author:
Thomas Pfau
